1. Our CEO falls in love with the petite Web Developer, Anamika Pandit. She now wants her last name to be changed to ‘Sharma’.
UPDATE employee_data SET l_name = 'Sharma' WHERE l_name = 'Pandit' AND f_name = 'Anamika';

l_name	f_name	title
Sharma	Manish	CEO

2. All Multimedia Programmers now want to be called Multimedia Specialists.

UPDATE employee_data SET title = 'Multimedia Specialists' WHERE title = 'Multimedia Programmer';

SELECT * FROM employee_data WHERE title = 'Multimedia Specialist';

emp_id	f_name	l_name	title	age	yos	salary	perks	email
